Scripts to radar ray tracing simulations using Nvidia Optix 8.0.0.
optixTriangle.cpp : modified optix example to setup BVH, pipeline, shader binding table and radar parameters.
optixTriangle.cu : Ray generation / hit / miss programs.
im.h : import of triangle mesh.

Billede_danner_GPU_bistatic.py : BPA function.
optixBPA_clutter4.py: BPA for optix simulation data.


